1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 17]

2
00:00:24,864 --> 00:00:26,063
Tell everyone

3
00:00:26,224 --> 00:00:27,383
my father has passed away.

4
00:00:28,544 --> 00:00:30,063
My condolences, young master.

5
00:00:53,624 --> 00:00:54,463
Mother?

6
00:00:59,064 --> 00:01:00,383
Is it really you, Mother?

7
00:01:01,624 --> 00:01:02,463
Yimo.

8
00:01:04,944 --> 00:01:05,863
All these years,

9
00:01:09,784 --> 00:01:11,783
I've thought of you every moment.

10
00:01:15,944 --> 00:01:18,063
Yet you never once visited my dreams.

11
00:01:19,584 --> 00:01:21,663
Though I couldn't see you,

12
00:01:23,064 --> 00:01:24,703
year after year,

13
00:01:25,064 --> 00:01:26,343
every moment,

14
00:01:26,864 --> 00:01:28,263
I prayed

15
00:01:28,944 --> 00:01:30,063
for your health

16
00:01:30,664 --> 00:01:31,383
and well-being.

17
00:01:32,584 --> 00:01:33,943
All these years,

18
00:01:33,944 --> 00:01:35,543
because of my death,

19
00:01:36,104 --> 00:01:37,383
you've been consumed by hatred,

20
00:01:37,384 --> 00:01:38,703
hurting yourself.

21
00:01:40,184 --> 00:01:41,183
Do you know

22
00:01:42,584 --> 00:01:46,263
I have endured heart-wrenching pain?

23
00:01:46,864 --> 00:01:48,463
Had I known earlier

24
00:01:48,584 --> 00:01:50,103
that my death

25
00:01:50,344 --> 00:01:52,543
would haunt you for so many years,

26
00:01:52,664 --> 00:01:54,543
I would have forgiven

27
00:01:54,704 --> 00:01:56,783
all who harmed me before dying.

28
00:01:59,104 --> 00:02:00,583
So my child

29
00:02:02,104 --> 00:02:03,863
could be free from resentment.

30
00:02:12,344 --> 00:02:13,823
I've been unfilial,

31
00:02:14,984 --> 00:02:16,183
causing you worry

32
00:02:17,184 --> 00:02:18,503
even today

33
00:02:21,544 --> 00:02:23,223
Now that you've avenged me,

34
00:02:25,344 --> 00:02:28,143
don't keep drowning in regret and pain,

35
00:02:28,144 --> 00:02:29,343
unable to find peace.

36
00:02:31,184 --> 00:02:32,303
Only then can I

37
00:02:33,064 --> 00:02:34,823
leave this cage

38
00:02:35,704 --> 00:02:37,063
that held my youth

39
00:02:37,864 --> 00:02:39,143
and find peace.

40
00:02:40,184 --> 00:02:40,703
Mother!

41
00:02:41,744 --> 00:02:42,823
Mother, don't leave!

42
00:02:42,984 --> 00:02:44,463
Don't leave me alone!

43
00:02:44,464 --> 00:02:45,343
Yimo.

44
00:02:46,304 --> 00:02:47,463
Life and death

45
00:02:47,464 --> 00:02:48,623
are never true separation.

46
00:02:50,504 --> 00:02:52,423
As long as you hold Mother in your heart,

47
00:02:53,624 --> 00:02:55,343
every snowfall hereafter

48
00:02:56,584 --> 00:02:58,583
will be my gentle breeze returning

49
00:02:59,304 --> 00:03:00,623
to visit you.

50
00:03:19,544 --> 00:03:20,463
What's wrong?

51
00:03:25,704 --> 00:03:27,903
I was just saying goodbye to my mother.

52
00:03:34,224 --> 00:03:36,063
Director Zhou, my condolences.

53
00:03:36,064 --> 00:03:39,303
Brother, why did you leave so early?

54
00:03:39,304 --> 00:03:41,223
What will become of me now?

55
00:03:41,224 --> 00:03:43,223
Nanxi, Director is heartbroken.

56
00:03:43,224 --> 00:03:44,463
It's understandable you didn't know.

57
00:03:44,584 --> 00:03:45,583
Director Zhou

58
00:03:45,584 --> 00:03:46,543
and Master

59
00:03:46,544 --> 00:03:47,583
were cousins.

60
00:03:47,984 --> 00:03:48,743
All these years,

61
00:03:48,744 --> 00:03:49,863
their collusion

62
00:03:50,064 --> 00:03:51,343
built their current status.

63
00:03:51,704 --> 00:03:52,823
Enough of this.

64
00:03:53,064 --> 00:03:55,183
Go to Wang's Pastry Shop in West Market.

65
00:03:55,184 --> 00:03:56,743
Buy a pastry box, understand?

66
00:03:56,744 --> 00:03:57,703
Get ox-tongue pastries.

67
00:03:57,704 --> 00:03:58,543
Master loved them.

68
00:03:58,704 --> 00:03:59,223
Yes.

69
00:04:00,864 --> 00:04:01,583
The eternal light?

70
00:04:01,864 --> 00:04:03,423
It's getting dark, we need it soon.

71
00:04:04,064 --> 00:04:05,583
It's in the blue box on that table!

72
00:04:05,824 --> 00:04:06,423
Fine,

73
00:04:06,424 --> 00:04:07,063
I'll get it myself.

74
00:04:17,584 --> 00:04:18,223
Steward.

75
00:04:19,104 --> 00:04:20,103
If I heard correctly,

76
00:04:20,624 --> 00:04:21,823
it's the blue box, right?

77
00:04:26,184 --> 00:04:27,583
You've accompanied the master for years.

78
00:04:27,944 --> 00:04:28,863
No matter how heartbroken,

79
00:04:29,184 --> 00:04:30,303
you must take care of your health.

80
00:04:31,104 --> 00:04:31,703
Understood.

81
00:04:32,544 --> 00:04:33,943
Thank you for your concern.

82
00:04:34,224 --> 00:04:34,823
Go ahead.

83
00:04:36,544 --> 00:04:37,743
I wish to be alone

84
00:04:38,944 --> 00:04:39,743
with the master.

85
00:04:40,104 --> 00:04:41,463
Then we'll trouble you.

86
00:04:56,224 --> 00:04:57,743
Lieutenant Yu from the Marshal's residence

87
00:04:57,744 --> 00:04:59,223
has sent twenty funeral wreaths

88
00:04:59,224 --> 00:05:00,543
to pay respects.

89
00:05:06,944 --> 00:05:07,583
You've lost weight.

90
00:05:08,464 --> 00:05:09,223
And look worn out.

91
00:05:11,424 --> 00:05:12,423
Thank you, Lieutenant Yu.

92
00:05:12,624 --> 00:05:13,583
Despite your busy schedule, you came

93
00:05:13,744 --> 00:05:15,423
to see Master Zhou on his final journey.

94
00:05:19,064 --> 00:05:19,623
It's only proper.

95
00:05:34,064 --> 00:05:35,423
I wish to burn some joss paper for him.

96
00:05:36,424 --> 00:05:37,303
I wonder if you

97
00:05:38,304 --> 00:05:39,103
could assist me?

98
00:05:40,944 --> 00:05:41,583
Certainly.

99
00:05:42,424 --> 00:05:43,543
With Master Zhou's passing,

100
00:05:43,944 --> 00:05:45,063
Marshal Lu targeting the Zhou family

101
00:05:45,064 --> 00:05:46,063
is inevitable.

102
00:05:46,744 --> 00:05:48,063
Zhou Yimo can't protect you.

103
00:05:49,064 --> 00:05:50,303
Thank you for the warning, Lieutenant Yu.

104
00:05:51,424 --> 00:05:51,863
Xiaoman.

105
00:05:53,104 --> 00:05:53,863
If you stay here,

106
00:05:54,704 --> 00:05:55,823
you'll face danger sooner or later.

107
00:05:56,744 --> 00:05:57,343
Come with me.

108
00:06:00,424 --> 00:06:01,423
The Zhou family's rise and fall

109
00:06:01,944 --> 00:06:02,943
means nothing to me.

110
00:06:03,864 --> 00:06:05,103
I have my own mission.

111
00:06:05,744 --> 00:06:07,423
But have you considered

112
00:06:07,624 --> 00:06:09,103
that those who collaborate with a tiger

113
00:06:09,744 --> 00:06:11,223
will eventually be devoured by it?

114
00:06:12,744 --> 00:06:13,623
So what?

115
00:06:14,224 --> 00:06:15,423
A fox borrowing a tiger's might

116
00:06:16,224 --> 00:06:17,863
captures prey more easily.

117
00:06:18,584 --> 00:06:19,303
Isn't that so?

118
00:06:21,424 --> 00:06:23,303
What brings Lieutenant Yu here?

119
00:06:24,104 --> 00:06:25,183
My father has passed away.

120
00:06:25,824 --> 00:06:27,623
Thank you for coming, Lieutenant Yu.

121
00:06:28,104 --> 00:06:29,543
Especially for burning joss paper

122
00:06:29,824 --> 00:06:31,463
with his concubine before my father.

123
00:06:32,464 --> 00:06:33,303
Thoughtful indeed.

124
00:06:37,304 --> 00:06:39,103
I came to pay respects.

125
00:06:40,064 --> 00:06:40,463
By the way,

126
00:06:41,744 --> 00:06:43,183
this is the Marshal's intention.

127
00:06:43,184 --> 00:06:44,223
The Marshal's intention?

128
00:06:44,584 --> 00:06:45,423
I've felt it.

129
00:06:45,944 --> 00:06:46,863
Then you should return quickly.

130
00:06:47,544 --> 00:06:48,463
Convey my gratitude

131
00:06:48,464 --> 00:06:49,623
to the Marshal promptly.

132
00:06:51,864 --> 00:06:52,463
Very well.

133
00:06:53,624 --> 00:06:54,223
Farewell.

134
00:07:00,744 --> 00:07:02,063
Persistent ghost.

135
00:07:02,824 --> 00:07:04,343
Worry about yourself first.

136
00:07:04,744 --> 00:07:05,423
Everyone

137
00:07:05,424 --> 00:07:06,743
is eyeing the Zhou family covetously.

138
00:07:08,104 --> 00:07:09,223
Fourth Concubine has returned.

139
00:07:29,024 --> 00:07:32,183
[Lin Youyi, Fourth Concubine]

140
00:07:39,424 --> 00:07:40,423
Eldest Young Master Zhou.

141
00:07:41,064 --> 00:07:42,103
It's been so long.

142
00:07:42,704 --> 00:07:43,583
Three years.

143
00:07:44,304 --> 00:07:45,543
You finally decided to return?

144
00:07:51,424 --> 00:07:52,543
After all, I am your father's

145
00:07:52,544 --> 00:07:54,743
properly wedded woman.

146
00:07:55,704 --> 00:07:57,543
Quite different from

147
00:07:57,544 --> 00:07:58,623
those messy affairs.

148
00:07:58,824 --> 00:07:59,623
Indeed.

149
00:08:00,464 --> 00:08:02,423
He was waiting for you before he died.

150
00:08:18,424 --> 00:08:19,103
Who is this?

151
00:08:22,864 --> 00:08:23,503
I'm Fifth Concubine.

152
00:08:24,824 --> 00:08:25,943
So young,

153
00:08:25,944 --> 00:08:27,623
yet you chose to become Master's concubine.

154
00:08:28,224 --> 00:08:29,063
To ward off ill omens?

155
00:08:30,224 --> 00:08:31,743
Doesn't seem

156
00:08:32,184 --> 00:08:33,423
very effective, though.

157
00:08:39,544 --> 00:08:40,983
You're right.

158
00:08:41,504 --> 00:08:42,663
It's my incompetence.

159
00:08:44,304 --> 00:08:45,503
My fate isn't strong enough.

160
00:08:47,304 --> 00:08:48,543
I failed to help Master

161
00:08:50,264 --> 00:08:51,903
avert this final calamity.

162
00:08:58,504 --> 00:08:59,863
There's really no need

163
00:08:59,864 --> 00:09:01,183
to blame yourself so harshly.

164
00:09:01,544 --> 00:09:03,383
I don't believe in superstitious nonsense.

165
00:09:03,624 --> 00:09:04,663
But he was quite convinced.

166
00:09:05,544 --> 00:09:06,063
Come.

167
00:09:06,504 --> 00:09:07,423
Kowtow to Father.

168
00:09:07,664 --> 00:09:08,743
Yes.

169
00:09:12,264 --> 00:09:13,543
What's wrong with these banners?

170
00:09:13,664 --> 00:09:14,623
One long and one short.

171
00:09:14,624 --> 00:09:15,423
So unsightly.

172
00:09:15,424 --> 00:09:16,543
I'll have them adjusted.

173
00:09:17,184 --> 00:09:19,263
Why is this cushion yellow?

174
00:09:19,504 --> 00:09:20,543
Change it for a white one.

175
00:09:20,544 --> 00:09:21,543
What were they thinking?

176
00:09:21,544 --> 00:09:22,623
Why not change it to red?

177
00:09:22,624 --> 00:09:23,263
Concubine Lin.

178
00:09:23,984 --> 00:09:25,543
Guests will be arriving soon.

179
00:09:25,744 --> 00:09:27,383
Attending to thesetrivial matters now might...

180
00:09:27,384 --> 00:09:28,863
The funeral hall represents the Zhou family's dignity.

181
00:09:28,864 --> 00:09:29,863
No carelessness allowed.

182
00:09:29,864 --> 00:09:31,543
Now that I'm back,

183
00:09:32,424 --> 00:09:33,623
you can rest properly.

184
00:09:33,984 --> 00:09:34,783
In terms of seniority,

185
00:09:35,184 --> 00:09:36,863
I should be managing this household.

186
00:09:39,504 --> 00:09:40,503
Right, Fifth Concubine?

187
00:09:42,544 --> 00:09:43,543
You're right.

188
00:09:44,184 --> 00:09:45,423
Since you've returned,

189
00:09:45,624 --> 00:09:47,263
we'll follow your arrangements.

190
00:09:48,864 --> 00:09:49,383
By the way,

191
00:09:50,264 --> 00:09:51,423
who are those people?

192
00:09:53,304 --> 00:09:55,503
Let me introduce them to you.

193
00:09:55,624 --> 00:09:56,423
These are

194
00:09:56,424 --> 00:09:58,263
senior members from the Zhou family shops.

195
00:09:58,544 --> 00:09:59,863
After Master's funeral,

196
00:10:00,064 --> 00:10:00,743
all of us

197
00:10:00,744 --> 00:10:02,623
need to discuss how to handle

198
00:10:02,624 --> 00:10:04,063
the estate he left behind.

199
00:10:06,184 --> 00:10:08,063
Since you're elders and seniors,

200
00:10:09,064 --> 00:10:10,183
I'll make proper arrangements.

201
00:10:10,184 --> 00:10:11,063
That won't be necessary.

202
00:10:11,424 --> 00:10:12,743
Steward has already handled it.

203
00:10:12,744 --> 00:10:13,423
Yes.

204
00:10:13,424 --> 00:10:14,183
Exactly.

205
00:10:15,624 --> 00:10:16,423
Also,

206
00:10:17,424 --> 00:10:19,063
I don't like how you address me.

207
00:10:19,984 --> 00:10:21,383
Call me Ms. Lin.

208
00:10:24,624 --> 00:10:25,903
Ms. Lin.

209
00:10:28,384 --> 00:10:29,543
It does sound better.

210
00:10:30,264 --> 00:10:30,903
Well then,

211
00:10:31,624 --> 00:10:33,623
Ms. Lin, perhaps you could call me

212
00:10:33,624 --> 00:10:34,543
Ms. Ye

213
00:10:34,904 --> 00:10:35,503
from now on?

214
00:10:47,544 --> 00:10:48,423
So Steward Xu is actually

215
00:10:48,424 --> 00:10:49,863
working for Fourth Concubine.

216
00:10:50,744 --> 00:10:51,743
We need to be careful with him.

217
00:10:52,744 --> 00:10:53,543
Ms. Ye.

218
00:10:58,304 --> 00:10:58,863
Coming

219
00:11:03,184 --> 00:11:03,903
Ms. Lin.

220
00:11:04,544 --> 00:11:05,423
Got a moment?

221
00:11:05,624 --> 00:11:06,623
I'd like to talk.

222
00:11:08,184 --> 00:11:09,503
But I'm a bit tired now.

223
00:11:27,184 --> 00:11:28,503
You like browsing books?

224
00:11:31,784 --> 00:11:32,903
I used to go to school.

225
00:11:34,064 --> 00:11:35,183
After my parents passed away,

226
00:11:35,184 --> 00:11:36,063
I had to drop out.

227
00:11:36,544 --> 00:11:37,503
I was just browsing.

228
00:11:42,984 --> 00:11:43,903
Please have a seat here.

229
00:11:44,504 --> 00:11:45,423
I'll pour you some tea.

230
00:11:47,544 --> 00:11:48,783
No need for tea.

231
00:11:49,624 --> 00:11:50,863
I'm a straightforward person.

232
00:11:52,144 --> 00:11:53,343
You're the fifth concubine.

233
00:11:54,504 --> 00:11:55,783
Now that the master is gone,

234
00:11:55,984 --> 00:11:56,623
according to tradition,

235
00:11:56,624 --> 00:11:58,063
you won't inherit much.

236
00:11:58,304 --> 00:12:00,183
The real contenders in this family

237
00:12:00,544 --> 00:12:01,983
are only me and Zhou Yimo.

238
00:12:03,624 --> 00:12:04,863
I understand that.

239
00:12:05,144 --> 00:12:06,303
For women,

240
00:12:06,304 --> 00:12:07,423
only by holding money in hand

241
00:12:07,424 --> 00:12:08,503
can one feel truly secure.

242
00:12:09,304 --> 00:12:10,623
Men are unreliable.

243
00:12:12,304 --> 00:12:13,783
Ms. Lin, what do you mean

244
00:12:13,904 --> 00:12:15,143
by saying that?

245
00:12:15,144 --> 00:12:16,503
I heard you and Zhou Yimo

246
00:12:16,504 --> 00:12:17,543
are quite close.

247
00:12:17,864 --> 00:12:19,143
But I've returned this time

248
00:12:19,304 --> 00:12:20,303
to compete with him

249
00:12:20,304 --> 00:12:21,383
for head of the family.

250
00:12:21,664 --> 00:12:22,783
If you side with him,

251
00:12:23,544 --> 00:12:24,863
once a man has money,

252
00:12:25,064 --> 00:12:26,303
he might ignore you.

253
00:12:26,504 --> 00:12:27,743
If you side with me,

254
00:12:28,184 --> 00:12:29,623
I'll give you a hundred thousand silver dollars.

255
00:12:29,864 --> 00:12:31,183
You'll be set for life.

256
00:12:34,624 --> 00:12:35,503
Ms. Lin

257
00:12:36,184 --> 00:12:37,423
you flatter me.

258
00:12:38,424 --> 00:12:39,503
As a mere concubine,

259
00:12:39,504 --> 00:12:40,783
how could I have any say?

260
00:12:40,904 --> 00:12:42,423
You didn't before.

261
00:12:43,184 --> 00:12:44,303
If you're willing,

262
00:12:45,184 --> 00:12:46,743
I can give you that standing.

263
00:12:47,384 --> 00:12:48,543
The master's will

264
00:12:48,744 --> 00:12:49,663
is useless.

265
00:12:50,744 --> 00:12:51,623
I have lawyers.

266
00:12:54,144 --> 00:12:55,303
Then I'll listen to you, Ms. Lin.

267
00:12:56,304 --> 00:12:57,623
Just as I thought.

268
00:12:58,544 --> 00:12:59,863
You're a smart woman.

269
00:13:00,184 --> 00:13:01,503
A hundred thousand silver dollars

270
00:13:01,504 --> 00:13:03,183
will be in your hands

271
00:13:03,184 --> 00:13:04,623
once I become head of the family.

272
00:13:10,064 --> 00:13:11,063
You heard everything.

273
00:13:16,064 --> 00:13:16,743
Zhou Yimo.

274
00:13:30,544 --> 00:13:31,983
Am I really that unattractive compared to

275
00:13:32,984 --> 00:13:34,543
a hundred thousand silver dollars?

276
00:13:37,064 --> 00:13:38,663
Who wouldn't be tempted by

277
00:13:39,544 --> 00:13:40,903
a hundred thousand silver dollars in cash?

278
00:13:44,064 --> 00:13:45,983
I'm a man who would die for you.

279
00:13:47,744 --> 00:13:49,143
Don't toy with me like this.

280
00:14:11,784 --> 00:14:12,983
You're free.

281
00:14:13,544 --> 00:14:14,543
But I'm yours.

282
00:14:26,904 --> 00:14:27,863
Silly.

283
00:14:28,624 --> 00:14:29,543
I'm not worthy.

284
00:14:52,144 --> 00:14:52,863
Heaven knows

285
00:14:53,544 --> 00:14:54,543
how worthy

286
00:14:55,264 --> 00:14:56,303
you are in my heart.

287
00:15:34,904 --> 00:15:37,183
You've always been in my heart.

288
00:15:37,504 --> 00:15:38,863
Otherwise, three years ago on New Year's Eve,

289
00:15:38,864 --> 00:15:40,863
I wouldn't have risked helping you escape.

290
00:15:40,864 --> 00:15:42,063
So what do you mean

291
00:15:42,064 --> 00:15:43,063
by telling me this now?

292
00:15:43,304 --> 00:15:44,063
Threatening me?

293
00:15:44,304 --> 00:15:44,863
Youyi.

294
00:15:45,184 --> 00:15:46,303
Now that my cousin is dead,

295
00:15:46,424 --> 00:15:47,543
I finally have a chance

296
00:15:47,544 --> 00:15:48,983
to take care of you and the children.

297
00:15:49,144 --> 00:15:50,423
I came back this time

298
00:15:50,424 --> 00:15:51,063
to fight for the position

299
00:15:51,064 --> 00:15:52,503
of head of the Zhou family.

300
00:15:53,544 --> 00:15:54,743
Let me ask you one thing

301
00:15:54,864 --> 00:15:55,743
Will you help me or not?

302
00:15:55,864 --> 00:15:56,543
I'll help you!

303
00:15:56,904 --> 00:15:57,743
Definitely!

304
00:15:57,864 --> 00:15:59,063
After all these years,

305
00:15:59,304 --> 00:16:00,903
don't you know what kind of person I am?

306
00:16:01,264 --> 00:16:01,983
Good.

307
00:16:02,184 --> 00:16:04,183
There are too many eyes watching.

308
00:16:04,864 --> 00:16:05,863
From now on,

309
00:16:06,064 --> 00:16:07,303
don't come to see me alone.

310
00:16:10,064 --> 00:16:10,543
By the way,

311
00:16:12,064 --> 00:16:13,903
that incident three years ago...

312
00:16:16,904 --> 00:16:18,423
there were no loose ends, right?

313
00:16:18,424 --> 00:16:19,303
None.

314
00:16:21,064 --> 00:16:21,983
But...

315
00:16:23,184 --> 00:16:24,903
that letter you wrote me...

316
00:16:25,904 --> 00:16:27,263
I couldn't bring myself to burn it.

317
00:16:29,864 --> 00:16:30,623
Zhou Quan,

318
00:16:31,184 --> 00:16:32,543
you didn't burn that letter?

319
00:16:33,624 --> 00:16:34,623
Don't tell me

320
00:16:35,304 --> 00:16:36,423
you kept it on purpose?

321
00:16:36,424 --> 00:16:37,543
How could that be?

322
00:16:38,184 --> 00:16:38,863
Youyi,

323
00:16:39,744 --> 00:16:40,663
that letter is

324
00:16:40,664 --> 00:16:42,543
evidence that could ruin my reputation.

325
00:16:42,904 --> 00:16:44,063
I just wanted to look at it

326
00:16:44,064 --> 00:16:44,903
when I missed you.

327
00:16:45,544 --> 00:16:45,903
Here's what

328
00:16:46,624 --> 00:16:47,183
I...

329
00:16:47,184 --> 00:16:47,863
don't worry.

330
00:16:47,864 --> 00:16:49,623
I'll burn it tonight.

331
00:16:50,264 --> 00:16:50,623
Here's what

332
00:16:51,544 --> 00:16:52,543
bring the letter with you tonight.

333
00:16:53,144 --> 00:16:53,743
Come to the backyard

334
00:16:55,424 --> 00:16:56,423
and meet at our usual spot.

335
00:16:59,064 --> 00:17:00,263
You don't trust me?

336
00:17:03,064 --> 00:17:04,463
I don't want to hear your empty promises.

337
00:17:04,744 --> 00:17:05,783
I only want to know

338
00:17:06,744 --> 00:17:08,223
what you can do for me.

339
00:17:09,584 --> 00:17:10,583
Fine.

340
00:17:10,984 --> 00:17:11,983
I'll bring it tonight.

341
00:17:11,984 --> 00:17:13,063
I'll do as you say.

342
00:17:13,224 --> 00:17:13,943
Fifth Concubine,

343
00:17:14,544 --> 00:17:15,743
what are you doing here?

344
00:17:17,464 --> 00:17:18,303
I wanted to bring Ms. Lin

345
00:17:18,304 --> 00:17:19,263
some pastries,

346
00:17:19,264 --> 00:17:20,463
but there seemed to be someone inside,

347
00:17:20,464 --> 00:17:21,343
so I didn't go in.

348
00:17:22,064 --> 00:17:23,063
I see.

349
00:17:23,824 --> 00:17:24,583
Such matters

350
00:17:24,584 --> 00:17:26,063
can be left to us servants.

351
00:17:26,064 --> 00:17:27,703
No need to trouble you, Fifth Concubine.

352
00:17:28,504 --> 00:17:29,343
In that case,

353
00:17:29,544 --> 00:17:30,383
I'll take my leave.

354
00:17:30,744 --> 00:17:31,743
Goodbye, Fifth Concubine.

355
00:17:37,304 --> 00:17:38,143
Steward Xu,

356
00:17:40,344 --> 00:17:41,303
what are you doing here?

357
00:17:42,104 --> 00:17:43,223
I brought some pastries.

358
00:17:43,744 --> 00:17:45,143
I don't like sweets.

359
00:17:45,664 --> 00:17:46,663
Steward Xu,

360
00:17:47,304 --> 00:17:47,983
did you forget?

361
00:17:48,464 --> 00:17:49,663
My memory is so bad.

362
00:17:49,664 --> 00:17:50,543
I'll change them for you.

363
00:17:50,544 --> 00:17:51,063
Wait.

364
00:17:51,704 --> 00:17:52,783
The lipstick colors in town

365
00:17:52,784 --> 00:17:53,703
are hideous.

366
00:17:54,304 --> 00:17:56,143
I wonder if it would be convenient for you

367
00:17:56,464 --> 00:17:58,063
to arrange for some Rogue Tears

368
00:17:58,144 --> 00:17:59,063
for me to take back?

369
00:18:00,264 --> 00:18:01,303
That might be...

370
00:18:05,544 --> 00:18:06,143
Alright.

371
00:18:06,784 --> 00:18:08,303
Since it's your request,

372
00:18:08,544 --> 00:18:09,463
then I

373
00:18:09,464 --> 00:18:10,743
will do my utmost to fulfill it.

374
00:18:13,504 --> 00:18:15,103
What is Rouge Tears?

375
00:18:20,664 --> 00:18:21,543
When my sister died,

376
00:18:21,704 --> 00:18:23,223
she was clutching Rouge Tears.

377
00:18:23,544 --> 00:18:24,543
All along,

378
00:18:24,544 --> 00:18:25,303
Rouge Tears

379
00:18:25,304 --> 00:18:26,703
was exclusively used by Second Concubine.

380
00:18:27,144 --> 00:18:28,463
Who would have thought Fourth Concubine

381
00:18:28,464 --> 00:18:29,343
also secretly obtained

382
00:18:29,344 --> 00:18:30,583
the right to use Rouge Tears.

383
00:18:31,104 --> 00:18:32,263
Perhaps after

384
00:18:32,944 --> 00:18:34,143
we find that letter,

385
00:18:34,144 --> 00:18:35,703
then we can unravel all the mysteries.

386
00:18:37,144 --> 00:18:38,823
I must get to the bottom of this.
